title: Homecoming Week: ‘We Are Bulldogs’ Oct. 5­-11 (California State University, Fresno)
text: ( Source : California State University, Fresno ) Fresno State will celebrate the theme ' We Are Bulldogs ' during Homecoming Week Oct. 5-11 with daily events - including the Associated Students Inc. T-shirt exchange program and campus decorating
